e2e/

# dist/ is NOT excluded: single-stage builds require dist/<app>/browser to be present
# in the build context (pre-built by bun run build:<app> before docker build).
# Multistage builds compile from source inside the build stage and never read dist/ from
# the host context, so including it here adds a small overhead but does not break anything.
